Esther Dankwah (amụrụ na ọnwa isii, 25, na afọ 1982) bụ onye Ghana na-agba ọsọ nke na-ahụ maka 100 mita
Ọ bi na Netherlands kemgbe afọ 2003.
O meriri ọla nchara na ndị otu African 4 x 100 mita relay team na afọ 2006 IAAF World Cup
Ya na ndị otu Ghana 4 x 100 mita relay team meriri nrite ọla edo na afo 2007 All-Africa Games na nrite ọlaọcha na afọ 2008 African Championships.
